Privacy Policy for QR Reader/Generator App

Effective Date: 29 May 2023

At QR Reader/Generator, we respect and value the privacy of our users. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and protect your personal information when you use our QR Reader/Generator app ("the App").

Information We Collect

We do not collect any personal information from our users through the App. We do not require you to create an account or provide any personally identifiable information, such as names, email addresses, or contact details.

Camera and Photo Access

Our QR Reader/Generator app requires access to your device's camera to scan QR codes However, please be assured that we do not access, store, or transmit any images or data from your camera.

Use of Personal Information

Since we do not collect any personal information from our users, we do not use or disclose any personal information for any purpose.

Data Storage

The App does not store any user data locally or remotely. Any QR codes generated or scanned using the App remain on the device and are not shared or transmitted to any external servers or third parties.

Tracking and Analytics

We do not use any tracking or analytics tools within the App. We do not gather any user data related to app usage, preferences, or behavior.

Advertisements

Our QR Reader/Generator app does not display any advertisements.

Data Security

We prioritize the security of your information. We implement appropriate security measures to protect any data processed within the App. However, please note that no method of data transmission or storage can guarantee complete security. While we strive to protect your information, we cannot guarantee absolute security.

Updates to Our Privacy Policy

We reserve the right to update or modify this Privacy Policy at any time. Any changes made to the policy will be effective upon posting the revised version within the App. We encourage you to review the Privacy Policy periodically.

Contact Us

If you have any questions, concerns, or requests regarding this Privacy Policy or our privacy practices, please contact us at mustafa@altinisik.net.

By using the QR Reader/Generator app, you agree to the terms and conditions of this Privacy Policy.
